0047|- [HelpText]
0048|*An automatic index with page numbers for selected keywords and phrases
0049|*is initiated by the control line
0050|*   - index <name_of_text_file> .
S   |            <                 >
0051|*The keywords must be indicated in the text either by putting a '*' as
0052|*a shadow character to any place within a word or by indicating
0053|*the start of a (longer) keyphrase by the shadow '[' and the end
0054|*of it by the shadow ']'.
0055|*The keysucro S simplifies typing of such shadow characters.
0056|*The resulting text file containing the key words and their page numbers
0057|*can be edited later. For example, it can be converted to a Survo
0058|*data file (by FILE SAVE), sorted (by FILE SORT) and edited (by FILE SHOW).
